{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji16.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致彭德怀电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年5月14日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报日军沿黄河增兵甚多，扬言渡河。又传日军于日前由平民抢渡，沿河民众甚为恐慌，西安粮价亦猛涨，正在疏散，人心惶惶。我军于此时机有在敌侧背给以打击以振奋国民党之必要，如何望告。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1941,"month":5,"day":14}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":72,"page_end":72},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}